videos.headline: Red Hawks QB dives into pylon for 1st score
videos.description: QB Gus Ragland dives into the end zone to give Miami of Ohio a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Johnson scores 2nd TD to tie game
videos.description: WR Anthony Johnson reels in a 20-yard touchdown to tie the game at 21-21.

videos.headline: Ragland throws another deep TD
videos.description: QB Gus Ragland chucks another deep touchdown pass, this one for 59 yards to cut the deficit.
